{"lastModified":1772738439154,"uri":"c::7655158652::vessel::0756fc80-f21d-11f0-90cb-c53e450681fd","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Mallorca, Balearic Islands\n\nMichisan is a contemporary Sanlorenzo SL90A motor yacht, designed to maximise space, light, and comfort through her innovative asymmetrical layout. This modern model showcases Sanlorenzo’s latest design approach, offering bright interiors and generous volumes throughout.\nShe accommodates up to 8 guests in 4 elegant en-suite cabins, while a professional crew of 4 ensures a seamless and enjoyable experience on board.\nHer exterior spaces are designed for relaxed outdoor living, with multiple seating and lounging areas ideal for socialising and dining al fresco. The spacious flybridge provides ample room for sunbathing and relaxation, while the aft deck offers a welcoming setting for outdoor meals. The swim platform allows easy access to the water, making time at anchor both comfortable and enjoyable.\nIn perfect balance, Michisan’s interior offers a refined and light-filled atmosphere, with a spacious main salon featuring comfortable seating and an indoor dining area. Large windows flood the space with natural light and enhance the connection to the sea, creating a calm and inviting environment for guests to relax and unwind.","blueprint":{"name":"MICHISAN","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::0756fc80-f21d-11f0-90cb-c53e450681fd::assets::d88ff140-f221-11f0-8645-97d410204221/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::0756fc80-f21d-11f0-90cb-c53e450681fd::assets::d892d770-f221-11f0-8646-97d410204221/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::0756fc80-f21d-11f0-90cb-c53e450681fd::assets::d88f06e0-f221-11f0-8645-97d410204221/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::0756fc80-f21d-11f0-90cb-c53e450681fd::assets::d8921420-f221-11f0-8646-97d410204221/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::0756fc80-f21d-11f0-90cb-c53e450681fd::assets::d8903f60-f221-11f0-8645-97d